rows.label: qst630402_msg0001
rows.name:
Bonard's squad was deployed to 
Temperantia to keep watch on the
Superbian Army.

rows.label: qst630402_msg0002
rows.name:
We know they passed their first
checkpoint at Aegishammer.

rows.label: qst630402_msg0003
rows.name:
You'll have to start out looking for
further clues on your own.

rows.label: qst630402_msg0004
rows.name:
I leave the rest in the capable hands
of the Hræsvelgr Mercenaries.

rows.label: qst630402_msg0101
rows.name:
Ah, you're back.
Have you found them?

rows.label: qst630402_msg0103
rows.name:
Well, that's a real blow. He was
a good man.

rows.label: qst630402_msg0104
rows.name:
If only we'd managed to get the
message to them...

rows.label: qst630402_msg0105
rows.name:
But you still managed to extract three
good men from a sticky situation. 
That alone is worth commending.

rows.label: qst630402_msg0106
rows.name:
I'll get the rest from Goffredo when we
debrief them. They should be back
soon.

rows.label: qst630402_msg0107
rows.name:
Thank you.
It seems your reputation 
is well-deserved.
